    {
      "id": "decision:M001:1",
      "label": "**Zod for domain model and configuration validation**: Using Zod provides both runtime validation and TypeScript type inference from a single source of truth.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/DECISIONS.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:2",
      "label": "**Pure Phase Engine**: Decoupling logic for calculating phase transitions allows for fast-forward catchup for reboots and deterministic testing.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S03/S03-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:3",
      "label": "**Smart Reconciliation with Drift Detection**: Maintain an internal `lastAppSetState` map. If a device's current state differs from the last state the app set, skip reconciliation.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S04/S04-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:4",
      "label": "**Lux sensor averaging (3-reading window)**: Filtering transient spikes using a rolling window ensures transitions are physically reliable.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S05/S05-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:5",
      "label": "**Pre-publish bit-depth verification**: Implementing a custom script to check PNG bit depth avoids store rejections that the official validator misses.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S08/S08-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:6",
      "label": "**SDK Decoupling**: Decoupling logic from the Homey SDK via a DeviceAPI abstraction was critical for achieving high test coverage (98 tests).",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S04/S04-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:7",
      "label": "**Validator Gaps**: The official Homey CLI validator does not check PNG bit depth, which is a common cause for human-review rejection.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S08/S08-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:8",
      "label": "**Catchup Safety**: Windowed evaluation in the PhaseEngine (clamped to 24h/4 iterations) successfully prevents infinite loops during reboot catchup.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S03/S03-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:9",
      "label": "**Delegated Validation**: Entry points (API/Flow) perform minimal logic and rely on the core App class to enforce state rules via shared schemas.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S07/S07-SUMMARY.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:10",
      "label": "**Pure Persistence Helpers**: Decoupled SettingsStore logic for config storage and validation enables full unit testing of the API layer.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/PROJECT.md",
      "confidence": "EXTRACTED",
      "sourceFile": "milestones/M001/M001-LEARNINGS.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision:M001:11",
      "label": "**PNG Bit-Depth Oversight**: Discovered that 16-bit PNGs pass `homey app validate` but fail manual store review; necessitated a custom byte-level checker.",
      "type": "decision",
      "description": "Source: .gsd/milestones/M001/slices/S08/S08-SUMMARY.md",
